# Design System

## Brand tokens

Primary (Rollin red): `#ca2527` → `hsl(var(--primary))` = `359 68% 47%`
Background: `#ffffff` → `--background: 0 0% 100%`
Surface/muted: `#f7f9fc` → `--muted: 220 33% 97%`
Text: `#3e4243` → `--foreground: 180 3% 25%`
Default theme: **light only** (no dark theme in v1).

## CTA rule

One `primary` CTA per screen. Use `variant="default"` (fills with primary).

```tsx
// ✅ One primary CTA per screen
<Button>Request Booking</Button>

// ❌ Multiple primary CTAs on same screen
<Button>Request Booking</Button>
<Button>Save</Button>
```

For secondary actions use `variant="outline"` or `variant="ghost"`.

## Layout & surfaces

- Pages sit on `bg-background`.
- Panels, cards, sidebars sit on `bg-muted`.
- Borders: always `border border-border` (1px). No heavy box-shadows.
- Focus: rely on `ring` (= primary) for accessibility, never remove `focus-visible`.
- Border radius: `--radius: 0.75rem` (12px). Use `rounded-xl` for cards/modals.

## RTL default

```tsx
// globals layout – Hebrew default
<html lang="he" dir="rtl">
```

Switch `dir` per locale.

- For Hebrew (RTL), the authenticated dashboard sidebar **opens from the right** (`side="right"` on `AppSidebar`).
- All margin/padding spacing must use logical properties or Tailwind `rtl:` variant when needed.
- Never modify shadcn primitives in `src/components/ui` to “fix” RTL; use layout wrappers and feature components instead.
